{"tid":281971,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"日本工業風 DULTON 好椅凳！七大武器之首","createTime":"2017-06-13T04:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T04:31:46.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23daadba95005d413f6ae64b6173520b5cdc01f7","tid":281971,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.saydigi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9d47e00c4d864e609b25ec9a24fa1a35.jpg?resize=640%2C427&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.saydigi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F9d47e00c4d864e609b25ec9a24fa1a35.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C427%26ssl%3D1&h=3f468df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n椅凳奧妙之處，是可以藏於民居之中，隨手可得，還可以坐著它來掩藏殺機，就算被警察抓到也吉不了你，真不虧為七種武器之首，因此家中擺著幾張椅凳也是很合理的，最近家裡重新裝修，也就順勢敗了兩張椅凳來防身。來自日本的家具雜貨品牌 DULTON 是我很喜歡的家居品牌之一，DULTON 是從代理非常知名的法國工業風品牌 TOLIX 起家的，透過長期接觸工業風元素與銷售經驗而發展出自有品牌，因此 DULTON 也有著濃濃的工業風設計與金屬元素。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>DULTON KITCHEN STOOL RAW</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4257/35099391742_70f056244c_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4257%2F35099391742_70f056244c_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=1a3a574f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入手的兩張都是凳子而非椅子，主要是為了方便移動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4221/35099384852_7a7c80b10c_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4221%2F35099384852_7a7c80b10c_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=5e57e97c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這張椅凳是可以透過旋轉椅腳來調整高度，另外說明一下，DULTON 的椅子是要自己組裝的，就跟 IKEA (是這樣唸嗎？我都唸IKEA)一樣，但組裝方式很簡單，主要就是把螺絲鎖上去而已，十幾分鐘就可以完成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4205/35099380712_754cd11bc7_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4205%2F35099380712_754cd11bc7_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=7b61edec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDULTON 的椅子都會有幾種固定的烤漆顏色，例如白、紅、灰、銀、咖啡等，我個人是偏愛鐵色，工業風的感覺更強烈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4273/34456654953_5fa67777c2_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4273%2F34456654953_5fa67777c2_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=647596e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鐵色的最大特色就是會有鏽斑，如果喜歡仿舊家具的人肯定很愛，因為椅子外層還有一層透明保護漆，所以生鏽的地方是不會接觸到的，也不太會繼續擴散。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4278/34878499890_6206ce17c8_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4278%2F34878499890_6206ce17c8_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=e3f442f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這張椅凳的線條很美，日本工業風和歐美工業風的設計風格還是有點差異，日本的工業元素比較沒那麼粗礦，反而細節設計上會比較豐富與柔和。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4282/35099367182_e0a54f69d5_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4282%2F35099367182_e0a54f69d5_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=f13a2f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但從設計上來看還是有向 TOLIX 致敬的味道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4266/35099363532_d2797f342a_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4266%2F35099363532_d2797f342a_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=5ab81bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為椅凳有著移動的便利性，平常除了可以拿來防身之外，更可以當作居家擺飾使用。"},{"pid":"90be8fabad1602728ca9bd208a8519ab3860bfda","tid":281971,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4215/35099359682_d1c5c09242_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4215%2F35099359682_d1c5c09242_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=dbc0f9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n植栽擺在椅凳上也是一種居家陳設方式，但建議盡量使用仙人掌，這樣防身效果更佳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4269/35135622891_43b5b6c9c5_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4269%2F35135622891_43b5b6c9c5_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=a6957661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前這張椅凳是拿來當作夫人的化妝椅使用，所以我都不敢惹她，以免帶來殺機。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>DULTON STOOL CLIPPER II RAW</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4196/35135619181_bbd4620dc8_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4196%2F35135619181_bbd4620dc8_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=76feffae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這張又是造型截然不同的 DULTON 椅凳，雖然乍看之下很像廟會或辦桌的圓形鐵椅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4269/34878477290_ecb8816339_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4269%2F34878477290_ecb8816339_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=e26d757c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣選擇了我最喜歡的鐵色，但這張的繡斑就沒那麼明顯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4278/34456629913_e179ae52fa_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4278%2F34456629913_e179ae52fa_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=296d39fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n螺旋式的椅座可以用旋轉方式來調整高度，這張椅凳的椅腳設計帶點前衛感，如果你有去過台中自然科學博物館，裡面有個超大的病毒模型跟這長得有點像。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4231/35135604811_bff8480a2e_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4231%2F35135604811_bff8480a2e_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=edaabd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這張椅凳的主要功用就是拿來坐，或者給幼兒當作汽車方向盤來玩，因為它的肌肉線條沒有上一張強烈，拿來擺設的話比較沒那麼出色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/farm5.staticflickr.com/4226/34456624363_031a81813b_z.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4226%2F34456624363_031a81813b_z.jpg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=04016fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結論就是，工業風的椅子通常都不太好坐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.saydigi.com/2017/06/dulton-stool.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saydigi.com%2F2017%2F06%2Fdulton-stool.html&d=uHgUlRXO4nbkmtt%2BWAbK4XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3924b4a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.saydigi.com/2017/06/dulton-stool.html</a>"},{"pid":"2a220a6ea406b260d619cb5b5f8f8d11fbb614b0","tid":281971,"uid":32661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">入手的兩張都是凳子而非椅子</span>，主要是為了方便移動。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩分別"},{"pid":"7463a592175fbe3e7611a930a9cdc2aaa00913c9","tid":281971,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">入手的兩張都是凳子而非椅子</span>，主要是為了方便移動。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n椅有pan 凳冇"},{"pid":"2931ac6436a7f1b3e2eb960a640d4541ee73ff43","tid":281971,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"dlton 勁多野睇，好多野都想搬返香港，而且d 野又唔係貴。<br />\nu<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/123024_e5f01c29483cac5625b88d05d9b5057b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F123024_e5f01c29483cac5625b88d05d9b5057b.jpg&h=f121afe3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}